    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "哈囉",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 2.2,
    "end": 6.46,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "各位衝A的戰士們我是彥君老師",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 6.66,
    "end": 11.46,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "解決了顯微鏡我們現在要縮小鑽進細胞裡了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 11.66,
    "end": 15.39,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "戰士們大家好我是曉臻助教",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 15.59,
    "end": 21.84,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "細胞構造雖然多但把它想像成一個工廠其實非常好記喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 22.04,
    "end": 26.85,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "第一個要看工廠的總理辦公室就是細胞核",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 27.05,
    "end": 31.62,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "它是生命中樞裡面藏著控制工廠的DNA",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 31.82,
    "end": 35.78,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師所有的細胞都有辦公室嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 35.98,
    "end": 38.58,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "會考陷阱來了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 38.78,
    "end": 43.98,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "原核生物像是細菌它們就沒有核膜包圍的辦公室",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 44.18,
    "end": 48.14,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "戰士們圈起來細菌沒有細胞核",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 48.34,
    "end": 52.55,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "接著看工廠的發電廠就是粒線體",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 52.75,
    "end": 57.87,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "它是行呼吸作用的地方負責把養分轉化成能量",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 58.07,
    "end": 62.52,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "所以活動力越強的細胞發電廠就越多",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 62.72,
    "end": 65.8,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "像是運動員的肌肉細胞",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 66.0,
    "end": 68.12,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 68.32,
    "end": 72.1,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "接下來是工廠的圍牆與大門",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 72.3,
    "end": 77.08,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "細胞膜負責控制物質進出它是全自動門",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 77.28,
    "end": 82.59,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "氧氣養分進來廢物排出去通通由它把關",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 82.79,
    "end": 86.86,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師那植物的細胞壁也是大門嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 87.06,
    "end": 89.03,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "不對",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 89.23,
    "end": 93.18,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "細胞壁只是固定形狀的厚圍牆",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 93.38,
    "end": 96.5,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "它沒有控制進出的功能喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 96.7,
    "end": 102.78,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "懂了細胞膜才是保全大叔細胞壁只是堅固的牆",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 102.98,
    "end": 107.34,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "接下來看植物工廠的特產葉綠體",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 107.54,
    "end": 112.78,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "它利用太陽能生產養分只有綠色植物細胞才有喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 112.98,
    "end": 115.46,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那工廠的倉庫呢",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 115.66,
    "end": 118.33,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "倉庫就是液胞",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 118.53,
    "end": 124.61,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "植物的液胞很大佔了細胞大半空間用來儲存水分與廢物",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 124.81,
    "end": 129.23,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "戰士們筆記植物液胞大動物液胞小",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 129.43,
    "end": 132.78,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "最後我們來做個大總結",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 132.98,
    "end": 138.41,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "動物植物都有膜、核、質還有發電用的粒線體",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 138.61,
    "end": 141.45,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "但只有植物有細胞壁",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 141.65,
    "end": 144.87,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "還有行光合作用的葉綠體",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 145.07,
    "end": 147.86,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "以及那個超級大的液胞",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 148.06,
    "end": 150.78,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們放下筆",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 150.98,
    "end": 155.38,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "閉上眼睛在腦海裡逛一次細胞工廠",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 155.58,
    "end": 161.88,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "閉上眼睛想一下喔如果我是一株仙人掌我的細胞裡會有細胞壁嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 162.08,
    "end": 166.89,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "仙人掌是植物絕對有細胞壁幫它支撐身體",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 167.09,
    "end": 171.22,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "漂亮完全正確",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 171.42,
    "end": 174.02,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "我是彥君老師",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
